\s IGIHE KIRASHITSE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Igihe kirashitse, \bd*\bd Nyen’indimo Yimbure\bd*\bd , \bd*\bd Uburo \bd*\bd mu kigega, urwamfu ruturirwe\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Urwamfu n’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd buro, vyabanye kuva kera; igihe kirashitse, bigira bitandukane./.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ivyo twigishijwe, maze tukavyizera, igihe kirashitse, tubibone n’amaso\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Abatizera bose, n’abank’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Imana bose; igihe kirashitse ntibazotubon’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ukundi./.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Abahizi mu kwizera basinziriye mu Mwami, igihe kirashitse tubabone n’amaso\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.N’umwami wacu Yesu, tumuzi mu kwizera; igihe kirashitse aho tuzomubona./.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ivyaremwe vyose vyama biraniha, vyifuza uwo munsi wo gucungurwa kwacu\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.N’imitima yacu, nayo iraniha, yifuza uwo munsi, w’ukuza kw’Umwami./.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Kaze Mwami Yesu turagukumbuye imitima yacu irakunyotewe\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Uzoza ryari ga Mwami Yesu, \bd*\bd Uzoza \bd*\bd ryari kutujan’i\bd*\bd  Muhira\bd*\bd ./.\bd*
